&lt;/table>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Figure 3 shows how the practice-specific tool mentors are&amp;nbsp;associated with practice tasks. Specifically, how to&#xD;
    associate practice-specific Method Composer tool mentors to practice tasks. The graphic on the left shows the&#xD;
    definitions of the task contributors (in the tool_guidance &amp;gt; method_composer &amp;gt; Tasks section). The graphic on the&#xD;
    right shows how a tool contributor is defined to add the &quot;tool to tool mentor&quot; associations&amp;nbsp;(the tool standard&#xD;
    category &quot;owns&quot; these relationships).&amp;nbsp;&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
